"menu. This can also be achieved from the *My Pipeline* page. To do so, "
"simply open the *CRM* app, or navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales "
"--> My Pipeline`. Either route reveals leads and opportunities on "
"the :guilabel:`Pipeline` page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/lead_enrichment.rst:96
